        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Strengthen And Fortify Existing Bridges Act of 2021 or the SAFE Bridges Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Transportation to establish a program to assist states to rehabilitate or replace bridges found to be structurally deficient. </p> <p>States shall use program&nbsp;funds for projects to rehabilitate and replace such bridges and to maintain their surface coating and corrosion protection systems.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
